---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Governance">
  <h1>Governance &amp; Transparency</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    Visio Nova Mundi is a Community Interest Company (CIC). We operate for public benefit and reinvest surplus into
    research, innovation, and community-focused initiatives aligned with our mission.
  </p>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card">
      <h2>Community benefit</h2>
      <p>
        Our activities are designed to deliver measurable improvements in service delivery, inclusion, and wellbeing outcomes.
        We work with partners to pilot solutions, evaluate results, and scale responsibly based on evidence.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Asset lock</h2>
      <p>
        As a CIC, we operate under an asset lock to ensure that assets and profits are used for community benefit.
        Surplus is reinvested into programmes and activities aligned with our public benefit objectives.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Transparency</h2>
      <p>
        We aim to operate with clear reporting, accountable governance, and responsible partnerships.
        Where appropriate, we publish summaries of outcomes, impact, and evaluation findings.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="card highlight">
    <h2>Our wider ecosystem</h2>
    <p>
      Visio Nova Mundi operates within a broader international ecosystem of independent commercial ventures led by the founder.
      Any surplus contributed from such ventures may be reinvested to support the CICâ€™s public benefit mission.
    </p>
    <p class="note">
      The CIC remains independent and operates with clear separation of governance, finances, and decision-making.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="bar">
    <div>
      <h3>Working with partners</h3>
      <p>
        We welcome partnerships with councils, public bodies, research institutions, and community organisations.
        Our approach is evidence-led, measurable, and designed for long-term sustainability.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/contact">Contact</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/work">Our work</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 40px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 90ch;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      align-items: start;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .highlight {
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(39, 99, 235, 0.06), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.06));
    }

    .note {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .bar {
      margin-top: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .bar h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .bar p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 80ch;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: white;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .btn.primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(39, 99, 235, 0.10), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.10));
      border-color: rgba(39, 99, 235, 0.25);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bar { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
